THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS (unmodified, included as permitted runtime components):

* runtime/interpreter/malbolge.c — reference Malbolge interpreter, Ben Olmstead
  (1998), placed by its author in the public domain.

* runtime/interpreter/Unshackled.hs — reference Malbolge Unshackled interpreter,
  Ørjan Johansen (2007–), placed by its author in the public domain.

Only their #include line / compiler flags were adapted for modern toolchains;
the language semantics are unmodified. See runtime/interpreter/PROVENANCE.md.
